      "content": "For 40 ÷ 10: start at 40, make jumps of 10 back to 0. Count: 40→30→20→10→0 — that's 4 jumps. So 40 ÷ 10 = 4. Each jump = one group of 10.",
      "cpa_phase": "pictorial",
      "visual_type": "number_line",
